    "plan_content": "Here's the full implementation plan:\n\n---\n\n## Plan: Add Stepper Compound Component\n\n### What I studied\n\nI read `carousel.tsx`, `tabs.tsx`, `accordion.tsx`, `spinner.tsx`, `utils.ts`, both registry files (exact line numbers), and example demos. All conventions are verified from live code.\n\n---\n\n### 4 changes total — 2 new files, 2 registry edits\n\n#### **File 1: `apps/v4/registry/new-york-v4/ui/stepper.tsx`** (CREATE)\n\nA pure-React compound component (no Radix UI) with:\n- **2 contexts**: `StepperContext` (activeStep + orientation) and `StepperItemContext` (step + computed state)\n- **2 private hooks**: `useStepper()` and `useStepperItem()` — both throw if used outside their provider (same pattern as `useCarousel()`)\n- **`cva`** for `StepperTrigger`'s 3 visual states — `completed` (filled circle), `active` (outlined primary), `pending` (muted outlined)\n- **7 named exports**: `Stepper`, `StepperItem`, `StepperTrigger`, `StepperTitle`, `StepperDescription`, `StepperSeparator`, `StepperContent`\n- `data-slot`, `data-orientation`, `data-state`, `data-step` attributes throughout\n\n`StepperSeparator` reads `orientation` from `useStepper()` and `step` from `useStepperItem()` — it fills (`bg-primary`) when `step < activeStep` (current step is completed), which is the standard UX convention.\n\n`StepperContent` returns `null` when `step !== activeStep`, acting as a conditional content panel.\n\n#### **File 2: `apps/v4/registry/new-york-v4/examples/stepper-demo.tsx`** (CREATE)\n\nInteractive 3-step horizontal demo with `React.useState(1)` for state. Steps: \"Account\" → \"Profile\" → \"Complete\". Triggers are clickable (jump to step), with Next/Previous buttons below.\n\n#### **Edit 1: `ui/_registry.ts`** — Insert after line 563 (between `\"spinner\"` and `\"switch\"`)\n```ts\n{ name: \"stepper\", type: \"registry:ui\", dependencies: [\"class-variance-authority\"], files: [{ path: \"ui/stepper.tsx\", type: \"registry:ui\" }] }\n```\n\n#### **Edit 2: `examples/_registry.ts`** — Insert after line 2124 (between `\"spinner-item\"` and `\"switch-demo\"`)\n```ts\n{ name: \"stepper-demo\", type: \"registry:example\", registryDependencies: [\"stepper\"], files: [{ path: \"examples/stepper-demo.tsx\", type: \"registry:example\" }] }\n```",
